@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "LoginFrame\n(View)" as View
participant "AuthController" as Controller
participant "AuthService" as Service
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over User, DB: QUY TRÌNH ĐĂNG NHẬP VÀ PHÂN QUYỀN

User -> View : 1. Nhập username & password
View -> Controller : 2. login(username, password)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. authenticate(username, password)
activate Service

Service -> DB : 4. Find TAI_KHOAN by username
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 5. Account Object
deactivate DB

Service -> Service : 6. Check Password (BCrypt/MD5)

alt Thông tin hợp lệ
    Service -->> Controller : 7. Auth Success (Role: ADMIN/NHAN_VIEN)
    Controller -->> View : 8. Chuyển hướng theo loai_tai_khoan
else Thông tin sai
    Service -->> Controller : 9. Auth Failed
    Controller -->> View : 10. Hiển thị lỗi: "Sai tài khoản/mật khẩu"
end

deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
@enduml